data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! MOTIVATED SELLERS! STUNNING 4-ACRE FARM OASIS ON THE TOP OF LAKE WAHA! 1999 Homesteaders paradise 3/2 home boast quarts countertops, master bath & walk in closet along with a family room, living room and dining area which leads out to the fully fenced backyard with a patio & above ground pool. Spacious 40x40 10 stall barn with four rooms & a large loft, a huge 24X36 shop, & a 24X24 detached double-door garage. Additionally, you'll find a 3-bay utility shed with two rooms and extended indoor stalls, along with an 80x24 high-tunnel indoor greenhouse, a chicken coop complete with an outdoor covered run, woodshed, plus more! With its fertile land and enclosed pastures, this property accommodates a wide range of livestock, not to mention horses as well as an abundance of crops, too many to list! Situated within arm's reach of fishing, boating, and hunting opportunities this remarkable farm property offers the perfect blend of rural tranquility and outdoor adventure. Schedule a showing today!
